DAY-8

Aaj ka kaam (User Progress Tracking & Learning Analytics)

1) UserProgress System Implementation
- UserProgressController banaya with nested user endpoints:
  - GET /api/users/{userId}/progress → user ka saara progress
  - POST /api/users/{userId}/progress → naya progress entry
  - PATCH /api/users/{userId}/progress/{progressId} → update progress
  - DELETE /api/users/{userId}/progress/{progressId} → remove progress

2) Progress Status Management
- Advanced progress tracking features:
  - PUT /api/users/{userId}/progress/by-topic/{topicId}/status → set status
  - PUT /api/users/{userId}/progress/by-topic/{topicId}/watch-seconds → update time
  - Automatic status updates based on watch time completion

3) Learning Analytics Methods
- UserProgressService me analytics functions add kiye:
  - getUserLearningProgressPercentage() → overall completion rate
  - getCompletedTopicsCount() → total completed topics
  - Progress streak calculation for motivation

4) Video Progress Integration
- Real-time video watching progress:
  - Watch time tracking in seconds
  - Automatic status change from NOT_STARTED → IN_PROGRESS → COMPLETED
  - Last seen timestamp for resume functionality

5) Security & Ownership Validation
- User can only access their own progress data
- Proper authorization checks in service layer
- Owner validation before any progress updates

6) Progress Status Enum Handling
- ProgressStatus: NOT_STARTED, IN_PROGRESS, COMPLETED
- Proper enum validation in controllers
- Status transition logic implementation

Testing Status
- Progress tracking working for individual users.
- Video watch time updates functioning correctly.
- Analytics calculations accurate.

Next Steps (DAY-9)
- ScoreCard system implement karna hai.
- Performance metrics generation add karna hai.
- Dashboard data aggregation karna hai.

